<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 18:08:19 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>日本首相告诉国会，美国的支持对乌克兰的生存至关重要</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-support-vital-for-ukraines-survival-japan-pm-tells-congress/articleshow/109224880.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109224880.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 15:59:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-support-vital-for-ukraines-survival-japan-pm-tells-congress/articleshow/109224880.cms</guid></item><item><title>印度裔美国人拉维·巴拉 (Ravi Bhalla) 在美国众议院民主党初选中获得大力支持</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/indian-american-ravi-bhalla-secures-strong-support-in-race-for-us-house-democratic-primary/articleshow/109223702.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109223702.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;新泽西州霍博肯市印裔市长拉维·巴拉(Ravi Bhalla)目前正在新泽西州第八选区角逐美国众议院民主党初选。在过去的几周里，他积累了强有力的支持和认可。如果巴拉在 2024 年 11 月的选举中取得成功，作为第一位在国会代表新泽西州的南亚人，将标志着一个历史性的里程碑。他还将加入已经在美国众议院任职的五名印度裔美国人的行列。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 15:26:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/indian-american-ravi-bhalla-secures-strong-support-in-race-for-us-house-democratic-primary/articleshow/109223702.cms</guid></item><item><title>特朗普攻击支持拜登的犹太选民：“应该检查他们的头”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-assails-jewish-voters-who-back-biden-should-have-their-head-examined/articleshow/109223812.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109223812.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;特朗普批评犹太选民支持拜登，将选举视为基督教实力测试。批评拜登对以色列-哈马斯战争的反应和对 LGBTQ 的支持。指出任何犹太民主党选民都需要接受“头部检查”。拜登承认国际跨性别者日。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 14:52:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-assails-jewish-voters-who-back-biden-should-have-their-head-examined/articleshow/109223812.cms</guid></item><item><title>庞贝古城出土的宴会厅壁画</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/banquet-hall-frescoes-unearthered-in-pompeii/articleshow/109220326.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109220326.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;考古公园周四表示，在庞贝古城出土了一座黑墙宴会厅，里面装饰着希腊神话中的场景，古罗马人在那里举行烛光盛宴。保存完好的壁画展示了阿波罗神试图引诱特洛伊女祭司卡桑德拉，以及特洛伊的海伦遇见帕里斯，这次相遇最终导致了战争。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 11:30:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/banquet-hall-frescoes-unearthered-in-pompeii/articleshow/109220326.cms</guid></item><item><title>捷克男子在西班牙加那利群岛拍摄巨浪时坠海身亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/czech-man-dies-after-falling-into-sea-while-taking-photos-of-huge-waves-in-spains-canary-islands/articleshow/109218014.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109218014.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;当局周四表示，一名捷克游客在加那利特内里费岛暴风雨中拍摄巨浪照片时掉入海中身亡。加那利群岛地方政府声明称，这名 53 岁男子周三下午在拉克鲁斯港镇死亡。救援人员从海中救起该男子，但不久后他就去世了。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 09:43:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/czech-man-dies-after-falling-into-sea-while-taking-photos-of-huge-waves-in-spains-canary-islands/articleshow/109218014.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国宣布制裁向台湾提供武器的美国公司</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-announces-sanctions-on-us-companies-for-weapon-support-to-taiwan/articleshow/109218423.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109218423.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国对两家美国公司实施制裁，因为它们据称支持向台湾出售武器，北京将台湾视为自己的地区。针对通用原子航空系统公司和通用动力陆地系统公司的处罚包括冻结其在中国境内的资产以及禁止其高管入境。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 10:34:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-announces-sanctions-on-us-companies-for-weapon-support-to-taiwan/articleshow/109218423.cms</guid></item><item><title>波兰立法者开始辩论废除近乎全面的堕胎禁令</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/polish-lawmakers-begin-debate-to-scrap-near-total-abortion-ban/articleshow/109218310.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109218310.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;波兰议会将就在这个天主教占主导地位的国家放宽堕胎法展开一场关键辩论。执政联盟的内部分歧暗示拟议的变革结果不确定。近年来，保守派政府领导下的妇女权利有所倒退，引发了对本已严格的堕胎法规的广泛抗议。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 09:58:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/polish-lawmakers-begin-debate-to-scrap-near-total-abortion-ban/articleshow/109218310.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦：俾路支学生会呼吁释放两名学生</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-baloch-students-council-calls-for-release-of-two-students/articleshow/109218111.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109218111.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;伊斯兰堡俾路支学生委员会发表了一封公开信，敦促释放拉瓦尔品第 PMAS-干旱农业大学的两名俾路支学生费罗兹·俾路支和艾哈迈德·汗。他们声称这些学生被关押在秘密拘留中心，凸显了俾路支省的压迫性条件。这封信还揭露了执法机构如何战略性地打压俾路支学生群体。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 09:47:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-baloch-students-council-calls-for-release-of-two-students/articleshow/109218111.cms</guid></item><item><title>马里军政府暂停所有政治活动，直至另行通知</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/malis-junta-suspends-all-political-activities-until-further-notice/articleshow/109217944.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109217944.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;马里执政军政府宣布暂停所有政治活动，直至另行通知，理由是需要维持公共秩序。这一决定是在去年推迟选举后于周三庆祝开斋节期间做出的。军政府发言人阿卜杜拉耶·迈加在国家电视台发表了这一声明。 2020年以来，马里经历了两次政变，掀起了席卷西非和中非的政治不稳定浪潮。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 09:41:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/malis-junta-suspends-all-political-activities-until-further-notice/articleshow/109217944.cms</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰议会通过一项有争议的法律，以增加急需的应征入伍者并填补军队军衔</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukraines-parliament-passes-a-controversial-law-to-boost-much-needed-conscripts-and-fill-army-ranks/articleshow/109217858.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109217858.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;乌克兰议会在经历了拖延和多次修改后批准了新的征兵法。这项由乌克兰军方发起、可能再招募 50 万军队的法律遭到了抵制。总统弗拉基米尔·泽连斯基 (Volodymyr Zelenskyy) 在 12 月强调了该法律的必要性。自俄罗斯全面入侵乌克兰以来，前线精疲力尽的士兵无法轮流休息，而数千名乌克兰男子则逃避应征入伍。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 09:37:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukraines-parliament-passes-a-controversial-law-to-boost-much-needed-conscripts-and-fill-army-ranks/articleshow/109217858.cms</guid></item><item><title>随着致命疫情的增加，您需要了解的有关百日咳的所有信息</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/all-you-need-to-know-about-whooping-cough-as-fatal-outbreaks-rise/articleshow/109217751.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109217751.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;全球百日咳再度流行，中国和菲律宾出现死亡病例。百日咳博德特氏菌会引起剧烈咳嗽。婴儿属于高危人群。如果尽早使用抗生素治疗。疫苗在中国、美国、英国有售。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 09:32:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/all-you-need-to-know-about-whooping-cough-as-fatal-outbreaks-rise/articleshow/109217751.cms</guid></item><item><title>联邦调查局担心俄罗斯大屠杀后美国可能发生协同袭击</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/fbi-concerned-about-possible-coordinated-attack-in-us-after-russia-massacre/articleshow/109217272.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109217272.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;联邦调查局局长计划周四告诉众议院小组，该局担心美国可能会发生类似上个月在俄罗斯音乐厅造成数十人死亡的有组织袭击。美国官员一直担心受以色列和加沙哈马斯战争影响的个人或小团体发动袭击的可能性。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 09:03:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/fbi-concerned-about-possible-coordinated-attack-in-us-after-russia-massacre/articleshow/109217272.cms</guid></item><item><title>第一位外国出生的相扑冠军去世，享年 54 岁</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/first-foreign-born-sumo-grand-champion-dies-aged-54/articleshow/109216834.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109216834.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 08:41:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/first-foreign-born-sumo-grand-champion-dies-aged-54/articleshow/109216834.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国宇航局宣布即将到来的日食和月食的令人兴奋的时间表</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/nasa-announces-exciting-schedule-of-upcoming-solar-and-lunar-eclipses/articleshow/109216457.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109216457.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国宇航局在全球范围内公布了一系列即将发生的日食和月食，为观测、摄影和科学研究提供了机会。在你的日历上标记这些罕见的天体事件。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 08:24:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/nasa-announces-exciting-schedule-of-upcoming-solar-and-lunar-eclipses/articleshow/109216457.cms</guid></item><item><title>“够了”：菲律宾就南海挑衅抨击中国</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/enough-is-enough-philippines-slams-china-over-south-china-sea-provocations/articleshow/109216374.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109216374.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;小马科斯总统领导菲律宾反对北京在南中国海的强势。最近的冲突涉及中国船只阻碍菲律宾海岸警卫队船只。美国提供支持，马尼拉计划寻求中国大使的澄清。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 08:19:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/enough-is-enough-philippines-slams-china-over-south-china-sea-provocations/articleshow/109216374.cms</guid></item><item><title>星球大战迫在眉睫：美国将军警告太空冲突威胁日益增加</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/star-wars-looming-us-general-warns-of-growing-space-conflict-threat/articleshow/109216038.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109216038.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;怀廷将军在太空研讨会上对俄罗斯和中国不断升级的太空能力发出警告，强调了对地球大气层之外潜在冲突的担忧。他强调迫切需要开展国际对话与合作，以防止太空冲突。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 08:11:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/star-wars-looming-us-general-warns-of-growing-space-conflict-threat/articleshow/109216038.cms</guid></item><item><title>“加州处于边缘：圣安德烈亚斯断层可能正在为大地震做好准备”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/california-on-edge-san-andreas-fault-may-be-gearing-up-for-major-earthquake/articleshow/109215683.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109215683.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;加利福尼亚州面临着与圣安德烈亚斯断层帕克菲尔德部分有关的迫在眉睫的地震。人们对历史地震、潜在损害和预测方法的进步表示担忧，强调了该州的地震脆弱性和防备工作。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 08:00:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/california-on-edge-san-andreas-fault-may-be-gearing-up-for-major-earthquake/articleshow/109215683.cms</guid></item><item><title>“大胆前行”：岸田首相在为美日同盟干杯时引用《星际迷航》</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/boldly-go-prime-minister-kishida-quotes-star-trek-in-a-toast-to-us-japan-alliance/articleshow/109215878.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109215878.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;白宫举行了盛大的国宴，纪念强大的美日同盟。拜登总统、岸田首相以及各位嘉宾在全球挑战中为持久的友谊和承诺干杯。此次活动强调了两国伙伴关系在解决全球问题方面的重要性，并重申了对民主、安全和经济增长的奉献精神。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 07:53:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/boldly-go-prime-minister-kishida-quotes-star-trek-in-a-toast-to-us-japan-alliance/articleshow/109215878.cms</guid></item><item><title>“达卡式悲剧”：前总理伊姆兰·汗对巴基斯坦发出可怕警告</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/dhaka-like-tragedy-ex-pm-imran-khans-dire-warning-for-pakistan/articleshow/109215369.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109215369.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;前总理伊姆兰·汗通过巴基斯坦正义运动党 (PTI) 将巴基斯坦目前的政治和经济动荡与 1971 年东巴基斯坦（现孟加拉国）分离的事件进行了类比。在国家新闻俱乐部举行的新闻发布会上，PTI 中央信息秘书拉奥夫·哈桑传达了汗的信息，强调迫切需要经济稳定来维护国家的完整性。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 07:26:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/dhaka-like-tragedy-ex-pm-imran-khans-dire-warning-for-pakistan/articleshow/109215369.cms</guid></item><item><title>大马士革袭击：伊朗与以色列冲突的新篇章</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/damascus-attack-new-chapter-in-iran-israel-conflict/articleshow/109215306.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109215306.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; 4月初，叙利亚首都大马士革的一座伊朗领事馆大楼遭到袭击，造成至少13人死亡，其中包括7名伊朗革命卫队高级成员。伊朗、叙利亚和俄罗斯指责以色列对此次袭击负责，但以色列本身并未对此事件发表评论。自从对加沙地带的哈马斯发动战争以来，以色列还加大了对黎巴嫩和叙利亚的伊朗代理人的攻击力度。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 07:22:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/damascus-attack-new-chapter-in-iran-israel-conflict/articleshow/109215306.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>